<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Of carmine clouds I think
while searching for
the flowing waters
of rejuvenation
Like structural colour
in the eyes of whom
shall not be named
indeterminate you are
Yet deep down I know
there will come a day
when you will tell us
where you went and why
nobody ever joined you
</code></pre></div></div>